export default COLORS;

export const ColorsByTheme = Object.keys(COLORS).reduce((accu, key) => {
  if (!key.includes('_')) {
    return accu;
  }
  const [theme, idx] = key.split('_');

  return {
    ...accu,
    [theme]: {
      ...accu[theme],
      [idx]: COLORS[key]
    }
  };
}, {});
